MOTION DOCKET

01-871. State v. Ahmed.

Belmont C.P. No. 99CR192. This cause is a death penalty appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Belmont County. On December 31, 2001, appellant, proceeding pro se, filed a document containing five motions. Whereas, on December 5, 2001, this court remanded this matter to the trial court for appointment of counsel,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that appellant’s document containing pro se motions be, and hereby is, stricken.
